These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, argentine, french, russian
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, snake, frog, fish
1. the owner of the fish is not to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##8
2. the owner of the fish is on the right of the indonesian##1
3. the argentine is on the left or right of the french##3
4. the russian is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
5. the russian is not to the left of the owner of the fish##8
6. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the argentine##5
7. the argentine is somewhere between the indonesian and the owner of the snake##7
8. the argentine and the owner of the fish have the same parity positions##9
9. the french and the owner of the chinchilla have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | indonesian | argentine | french     | russian |
| Pet           | frog   | fish     | snake | chinchilla  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, iced-tea, juice, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, chess, gardening, reading
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is reading and the person drinking iced-tea have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's hobby is chess is not to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##8
4. the person who's hobby is writing is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
5. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
6. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5
7. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
8. the person drinking water is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | water     | juice    | milk | iced-tea    |
| Hobby      | writing | chess | gardening      | reading |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, water, tea, iced-tea
There 4 different types of food: pepper, apple, watermelon, asparagus
1. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person eating watermelon##5
2. the person eating pepper is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
3. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
7. the person eating pepper is not to the left of the person eating apple##8
8. the person drinking water and the person eating apple have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | water    | tea   | sprite    | iced-tea  |
| Food       | apple | asparagus | pepper | watermelon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, mechanic, writer, electrician
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, disco, d&b, classical
1. the fan electronic is the mechanic##1
2. the fan disco is on the right of the fan d&b##1
3. the fan disco is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
4. the fan classical is on the left or right of the writer##3
5. the fan disco is on the left of the architect##1
6. the electrician and the fan classical have the same parity positions##9
7. the writer is on the left or right of the architect##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | electrician | writer | architect  | mechanic |
| Music-Genre   | d&b             | disco          | classical | electronic    |

