.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, jazz, indie, soul
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, goat, snake, mouse
1. the fan indie is not the owner of the snake##6
2. the owner of the guinea-pig and the fan salsa have different parity positions##9
3. the owner of the goat and the fan jazz have different parity positions##9
4. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the fan indie##5
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the fan soul##1
6. the fan jazz is not the owner of the goat##6
7. the fan soul is somewhere to the left of the fan jazz##5
8. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the fan salsa##1
9. the owner of the mouse is not the fan soul##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | indie | soul  | jazz |
| Pet           | goat   | guinea-pig     | snake | mouse      |

