.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, spy, sports, drama
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, argentine, spanish, chinese
1. the person watching spy movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the spanish is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
4. the canadian and the person watching sports movies have the same parity positions##9
5. the person watching drama movies and the canadian have different parity positions##9
6. the spanish is not to the left of the person watching zombie movies##8
7. the chinese is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5
8. the person watching spy movies is not to the right of the chinese##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | zombie | sports | drama |
| Nationality   | chinese        | spanish    | canadian   | argentine |

