4. the coach is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the police-officer##5
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |  2   |     3     |      4       |
| Job   | mechanic | writer | coach | police-officer |
| Pet   | rabbit         | guinea-pig | bird    | goldfish   |

