2. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's sport is tennis##2
3. the person who's sport is rowing and the fan country have different parity positions##9
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
5. the fan country is not to the right of the fan metal##8
6. the fan trance is somewhere to the left of the fan metal##5
7. the fan country is somewhere to the right of the fan r&b##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | trance | country         | metal     |
| Sport         | swimming | rowing  | tennis | golf |

