.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, sudoku, puzzles, writing
4 different pets are kept: lizard, horse, guinea-pig, hedgehog
1. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere between the owner of the lizard and the owner of the horse##7
2. the owner of the horse is not to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##8
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not the owner of the lizard##6
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##5
7. the person who's hobby is writing and the owner of the hedgehog have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | writing | sudoku | camping | puzzles |
| Pet     | horse     | guinea-pig     | hedgehog     | lizard    |

