.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-10::.
There 4 different types of food: peach, strawberry, eggplant, cabbage
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, van, roller, airplane
1. the person driving the airplane is not to the left of the person eating peach##8
2. the person eating cabbage and the person driving the airplane have the same parity positions##9
3. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the person driving the roller##5
4. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
5. the person eating strawberry is somewhere between the person driving the van and the person driving the airplane##7
6. the person eating cabbage is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | eggplant | peach   | strawberry | cabbage |
| Transport   | roller   | van | skateboard    | airplane      |

