.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-11::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, pineapple, apricot, spinach
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, woodworking, video-games, baking
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
2. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is the person eating spinach##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person eating apricot have different parity positions##9
5. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |      3       |     4     |
| Food    | spinach | onion | pineapple   | apricot   |
| Hobby   | baking  | video-games   | woodworking | drawing |

