.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-12::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, electronic, r&b, soul
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, snowmobile, subway, jet-ski
1. the fan funk is on the right of the fan r&b##1
2. the fan r&b is not to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##8
3. the fan soul and the person driving the snowmobile have the same parity positions##9
4. the person driving the jet-ski is the fan soul##1
5. the fan funk is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bus##5
6. the person driving the subway is on the left of the fan soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |   3   |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | electronic  | soul  | r&b | funk    |
| Transport     | subway | jet-ski | bus  | snowmobile |

