.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-13::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, pepper, pomegranate, radish
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, malaysian, british, chinese
1. the person eating radish is not the chinese##6
2. the chinese is not to the right of the pakistani##8
3. the person eating pomegranate is not to the left of the person eating radish##8
4. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person eating pepper##3
5. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the british##3
6. the chinese is on the far left##1
7. the pakistani is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
8. the person eating grapefruit is the malaysian##1
9. the person eating radish and the pakistani have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | pepper   | radish    | pomegranate | grapefruit    |
| Nationality   | chinese | pakistani | british   | malaysian |

