The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, folk, house, rock
1. the person eating kale and the fan rock have the same parity positions##9
2. the fan rock is not to the left of the person eating kale##8
3. the person eating lime is somewhere between the fan reggae and the fan rock##7
4. the fan rock is somewhere between the fan house and the person eating lime##7
5. the fan folk is not the person eating papaya##6
6. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating lime##1
7. the person eating lemon is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | papaya | lime | kale | lemon  |
| Music-Genre   | reggae    | folk | rock | house |

