The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, satire, martial-arts, sports
1. the person watching musical movies is not the person drinking cola##6
2. the person drinking cola is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
4. the person watching satire movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
6. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
8. the person watching musical movies and the person drinking water have the same parity positions##9
9. the person watching martial-arts movies and the person drinking lemonade have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | cola   | coffee  | lemonade  | water |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | martial-arts | sports | musical      |

