.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate, fanta, sprite
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, d&b, pop, rock
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate and the fan pop have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person drinking fanta is not to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
 3. the fan electronic is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking juice##7
 4. the fan pop is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
 5. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan pop is not to the left of the person drinking sprite##8
 7. the person drinking sprite and the fan d&b have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the fan rock##3
 9. the fan rock is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking sprite is not to the right of the fan electronic##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | juice  | sprite | fanta  | hot-chocolate |
| Music-Genre   | rock | pop     | electronic | d&b     |

