4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, bird, pony, turtle
1. the engineer and the owner of the guinea-pig have the same parity positions##9
2. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
3. the analyst is not to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##8
4. the engineer is not to the right of the software-developer##8
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the pony and the fisherman have the same parity positions##9
7. the owner of the guinea-pig and the analyst have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |   2    |     3      |       4        |
| Job   | fisherman | engineer | software-developer | analyst |
| Pet   | pony    | bird   | turtle        | guinea-pig            |

