.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, lemonade, almond-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, woodworking, writing, camping
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is camping is not to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##8
 4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is video-games is not the person drinking fanta##6
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the person drinking 7up##8
 7. the person drinking almond-milk and the person who's hobby is woodworking have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking fanta is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
10. the person drinking fanta and the person who's hobby is woodworking have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | fanta    | lemonade        | almond-milk   | 7up      |
| Hobby      | camping | writing | woodworking | video-games |

 